1.title: Smokepurpp/Spike Lee

episode of.title: Open Late with Peter Rosenberg (TV Series 2018– )

1.plot: Smokepurpp sits down with Peter Rosenberg to discuss his upcoming collab album with Travis Barker, the deaths of XXXTentacion and Lil Peep and how his drug use has changed. Plus, Amanda Seales and Cipha Sounds join Rosenberg to break down Travis Scott's place in the game, whether or not Drake has a classic and more. And Mouse Jones has an awkward and one-of-a-kind interaction with Spike Lee.

2.title: YBN Gang

episode of.title: Open Late with Peter Rosenberg (TV Series 2018– )

2.plot: Rosenberg sits down with YBN Gang -- Nahmir, Cordae and Almighty Jay -- to hear about their relationship, rise, influences and more. Plus, Jinx and Scottie Beam join to break down Nicki Minaj's "Queen" album, Omarosa and Eminem vs. Andre 3000. And, as always, araabMUZIK is on the MPC.

3.title: The New Day/Sasha Banks

episode of.title: Open Late with Peter Rosenberg (TV Series 2018– )

3.plot: This week's WWE-filled "Open Late" features a lively discussion with Kofi Kingston, Big E and Xavier Woods of the New Day. Sasha Banks also joins host Peter Rosenberg in the studio for a candid conversation about her life and career. And Peter and his wife Alexa go on a double date with Lana and Rusev. Plus, araabMUZIK is on the MPC.

4.title: Amber Rose

episode of.title: Open Late with Peter Rosenberg (TV Series 2018– )

4.plot: Rosenberg catches up with Amber Rose at her house in Los Angeles to . hear about her relationship Monte Morris, how Nicki Minaj ended up on Kanye West's "Monster," and more. Plus, Trinidad James and Shani Kulture join Rosenberg in the studio to talk about their favorite hip-hop movies and rank their all-time icons of hip-hop fashion. Then, Kodie Shane performs her single "Sing to Her."

5.title: Shiggy/Lil Rel Howery/Chad Ochocinco

episode of.title: Open Late with Peter Rosenberg (TV Series 2018– )

5.plot: Rosenberg sits down with Lil Rel and Chad Ochocino to break down the future of Colin Kaepernick and the NFL, Eminem's new album, Kamikaze, and more. Then, comedian and viral sensation Shiggy stops by to talk about his whirlwind summer, meeting Drake and starring in the "In My Feelings" video. Plus, "Everyday Struggle" host Wayno catches up with Pusha T, Lil B, BlocBoy JB and more at Made in America. And, as always, araabMUZIK is in the building.

6.title: Mac Miller Tribute

episode of.title: Open Late with Peter Rosenberg (TV Series 2018– )

6.plot: Rosenberg is joined in-studio by Smoke DZA, Jeff and Eric Rosenthal (ItsTheReal) and Craig Jenkins to remember their friend and collaborator. Plus, Kendrick Lamar, Machine Gun Kelly, Ty Dolla $ign, Macklemore and Lil Xan offer their heartfelt remembrances.

7.title: Famous Dex/Rico Nasty

episode of.title: Open Late with Peter Rosenberg (TV Series 2018– )

7.plot: Famous Dex stops by to talk about his debut album, relationship with Rich the Kid, wild energy, fatherhood and more. Then, Rosenberg heads uptown to get pedicures with Rico Nasty. Plus, Lala Anthony and Jess Hilarious weigh in on the week's news, and, as always, araabMUZIK is in the building.

8.title: Lil Xan/Curren$y

episode of.title: Open Late with Peter Rosenberg (TV Series 2018– )

8.plot: Lil Xan stops by to talk about his recent Cheetos health scare, his break-up with Noah Cyrus, 2Pac, Mac Miller and more. Then, Rosenberg links up with Curren$y for a freestyle in the park. Plus, Dave East and Styles P weigh in on the week's news.

9.title: Blac Youngsta/Bas

episode of.title: Open Late with Peter Rosenberg (TV Series 2018– )

9.plot: Blac Youngsta and Bas weigh in on Lil Wayne's "Tha Carter V," what rap group they'd like to reunite, and more. Then, araabMUZIK gets in the studio with Mike Posner to cook up some magic from scratch. Plus, Gashi stops by to talk about his incredible come up, signing with Roc Nation and more.

10.title: Anderson.Paak/Ric Flair

episode of.title: Open Late with Peter Rosenberg (TV Series 2018– )

10.plot: Rosenberg sits down with Anderson .Paak to discuss his upcoming album "Oxnard," his special relationship with Mac Miller and more. Plus, Joey Purp and Torae stop by for some heated debate about the week's news, from Vic Mensa and XXXTentacion to Quavo's new album and the future of Migos. Then, Rosenberg he goes Rolex shopping with the legendary Ric Flair. And, as always, araabMUZIK is in the building.

11.title: Kris Wu

episode of.title: Open Late with Peter Rosenberg (TV Series 2018– )

11.plot: This week, Rosenberg steps on the court with Kris Wu to go one-on-one to see whose game is better, all while while Kris opens up about his music career and new album. Then, Roy Wood Jr. and Laura Stylez weigh in on the latest with Kanye West, Drake opening up about his feud with Pusha T, and LeBron James' future outside of basketball. Plus, araabMUZIK is on the MPC.

12.title: G Herbo

episode of.title: Open Late with Peter Rosenberg (TV Series 2018– )

12.plot: Rosenberg sits down with G Herbo to hear about his plans to drop more music with Southside, his recent conversation with Kanye West, giving back in Chicago, Vic Mensa's BET Hip-Hop Awards freestyle and more. Then, Racks and DJ Kast One join to break down recent headlines, including 50 Cent going at Ashanti and Wiz Khalifa's upcoming R&B album.

13.title: Action Bronson/ItsTheReal

episode of.title: Open Late with Peter Rosenberg (TV Series 2018– )

13.plot: Action Bronson stops by to talk about his new album, "White Bronco," why he's parting ways with VICE, a memorable edibles experience and more. Then, Jeff and Eric Rosenthal from ItsTheReal break down the latest with Nicki Minaj and Cardi B, Tyga's career resurgence and their favorite moments so far this year. Plus, araabMUZIK builds some beats on the MPC.

14.title: Michael B. Jordan

episode of.title: Open Late with Peter Rosenberg (TV Series 2018– )

14.plot: "Open Late" is switching things up and headed to ComplexCon. Peter Rosenberg sits down with Emmy-nominee Michael B Jordan to chat Black Panther, the upcoming Creed II, and why he's getting politically active this year. As always, AraabMuzik holds it down on the MPCs.

15.title: G-Eazy

episode of.title: Open Late with Peter Rosenberg (TV Series 2018– )

15.plot: "Open Late" is switching things up and headed to ComplexCon. Peter Rosenberg sits down with platinum recording artist G-Eazy to chat about his latest tour, the passing of Mac Miller, and what it's like to meet Rihanna. As always, AraabMuzik holds it down on the MPCs.

1.title: ASAP Rocky

episode of.title: Open Late with Peter Rosenberg (TV Series 2018– )

1.plot: On the premiere of Open Late with Peter Rosenberg, Peter breaks down Cardi B's rise. A$AP Rocky shares his thoughts on Travis Scott, his relationship with Kanye and his new album. Plus, Rich The Kid performs, "Plug Walk."

2.title: Terry Crews

episode of.title: Open Late with Peter Rosenberg (TV Series 2018– )

2.plot: On the second episode of "Open Late with Peter Rosenberg," Peter claims that we're living through hip-hop's Golden Age, and his panel of Miss Info, Damien Scott and Mouse Jones weigh in. Then, Terry Crews gets real about masculinity and his love for Kendrick Lamar and Public Enemy. Plus, Smoke DZA performs his new track "The Hustle" with Bodega Bamz and LevyGrey.

3.title: Lil Yachty

episode of.title: Open Late with Peter Rosenberg (TV Series 2018– )

3.plot: Lil Yachty stops by to talk about why he's rapping more on Lil Boat 2, his gift-giving tendencies, his admiration for Donald Glover and more. Plus, Bridget Kelly, Ebro Darden, and Rembert Browne join Rosenberg on the panel to break down and work through Kanye West's recent tweet spree and professions of love and admiration for Donald Trump. And araabMUZIK performs a one-of-a-kind set.

episode of.title: Open Late with Peter Rosenberg (TV Series 2018– )

Then, Bhad Bhabie talks about her rise and addresses criticisms against her. Rosenberg also sits down with Nick Cannon, to talk about his activism, new music and more. Plus, Desiigner, performs his new song "Priice Tag."

6.title: Pete Davidson/Ace Hood

episode of.title: Open Late with Peter Rosenberg (TV Series 2018– )

6.plot: Pete Davidson joins Peter Rosenberg for a hilarious conversation on the latest episode of "Open Late," touching on everything from his time in rehab, Donald Trump's appearance on "SNL," and his love for Kid Cudi. Plus, Lil Baby, Stalley and Nadeska Alexis join Rosenberg on the panel to break down some of the week's biggest headlines. Plus, Rosenberg also faces off with Ace Hood in a smoothie-making battle for the ages.

7.title: Kyle/Belly

episode of.title: Open Late with Peter Rosenberg (TV Series 2018– )

Plus, Denzel Curry, HoodCelebrityy and Zaytoven join the panel to discuss the Billboard Music Awards and allegations against R. Kelly. And Belly kicks a crazy freestyle in the latest "Bear with Me."
